  <title>Mon and Chloes Stir Fried Noodles</title>
  <filename>mon_chloes_stir_fried_noodles.xml</filename>
  <thumbnail>chloes_fried_noodles.jpeg</thumbnail>
  <category/>
  <yield/>
  <prepTime>PT0M</prepTime>
  <cookTime>PT0M</cookTime>
  <comment/>
  <ingredient>Flat rice noodles </ingredient>
  <ingredient>Stir Fries Veggies</ingredient>
  <ingredient>Bean shoots</ingredient>
  <ingredient>Coriander 1/4 cup chopped</ingredient>
  <ingredient>4 onions chopped </ingredient>
  <ingredient>2 cloves crushed</ingredient>
  <ingredient>Oil</ingredient>
  <ingredient>Sauce</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1/4 cup soy sauce</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1 TBsp each sweet chilli, fish, oyster sauce</ingredient>
  <ingredient>1/2 lime juiced</ingredient>
  <step>Make sauce and set aside.</step>
  <step>Cook noodles per packet direction, then set aside.</step>
  <step>Heat wok and heat a small amount of oil.</step>
  <step>Cook the garlic for 3 minutes.</step>
  <step>Place veggies in pan and stir fry until veggies cooked.</step>
  <step>Place noodles in the pan with the sauce.</step>
  <step>Stir together until blended and heated through.</step>
  <step>Serve with bean shoots, spring onion and coriander sprinkled on top.</step>
</recipe>
